Bricks Restaurant & Patio Bar Micanopy/Macintosh is now Available for public and private rentals.  Our space has a full bar & Restaurant, full audio/video system, and covered patio. We can accommodate any event you can dream of, from corporate meetings, to company mixers and even birthday celebrations.
Private Event For Weekends
Thursday-Saturday $4,000 Open Bar Private Party.
The private party fee includes rental and gratuity for up to 70 guests, 3 bartenders, and a dedicated floor staff member to make sure everything goes right.
NO HIDDEN FEES
Outside catering is allowed. 10% Deposit required. No Refund.
Private Event for Weekdays
Sunday-Wednesday $3,000 8pm-Close Open Bar Private Party
Private party fee includes rental and gratuity for up to 70 guests, 2 bartenders and a dedicated floor staff member to make sure everything goes right.
NO HIDDEN FEES
Outside food catering is allowed. 10% Deposit required. No refund.
Smaller Events
If you have 15 or more guests, we can host your event on our exclusive venue side from 4-7pm Monday-Friday for a $500 bar guarantee plus 20% tip guarantee for the bartender (That means if your guests don’t buy $500 in booze you pay the difference and make sure the total amount in tips = $100). Totally Win Win.
Saturday we can open at 1pm. 1-7 is available for a $1000 bar guarantee. 1-4pm for a $500 bar guarantee.
Sunday 1-4pm is available for $500. After 4pm please contact for rates
Also, we can do open bar for you on a credit card. You can tell us the amount you are willing to spend, or keep track of total sales to your party and make sure to add 20% Gratuity.
No deposit required unless there is an event already scheduled that needs to be rescheduled.
Free Birthday Parties
For questions or reservations please contact:
Lawrenceclay@gmail.com or Call 424.666.9359
.entry-content

Bricks Restaurant & Patio Bar Micanopy
is the perfect place to enjoy the best experience. Whether you visit us for brunch to start your day on a Sunday or join us $15 Burger & Beer Night on Fridays you can rest assured that you’ll have a fantastic time. We aim to create an unforgettable experience for all our guests.
I
GET A GREAT EXPERIENCE AT THE RIGHT PRICE
When visiting our venue you can always find fantastic deals daily. We offer the best deals to let you experience the food and drinks you want for less. We also welcome you for all day breakfast.
Our Food
Social friendly quick fix for Mexican & American mainstays topped with our signature sauces.
